	<h1 id="main-heading">KRS ยง 189.290 - Operator of vehicle to drive carefully</h1>

	<ol class="flow law-definitions">
		<li>The operator of any vehicle upon a highway shall operate the vehicle in a careful manner, with regard for the safety and convenience of pedestrians and other vehicles upon the highway.</li>
		<li>No person shall willfully operate any vehicle on any highway in such a manner as to injure the highway.</li>
	</ol>

